about.pageTitle: About | Advantage Seal | The Seal of Quality
about.pageDescription: Advantage Seal is a professional manufacturer of mechanical seals, which integrates R&D, production and sales. It is a high-tech enterprise with a history of more than 20 years. The company has a strong technical force, advanced production equipment, perfect testing methods and a complete quality management system. The company has passed ISO9001:2015 quality management system certification, and its products have passed CE certification. The company's products are widely used in petroleum, chemical, metallurgy, electric power, papermaking, pharmaceutical, food, mining, water treatment and other industries.
